OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FDuring the NHS Providers conference in
OL,7,FLiverpool, Wes Streeting told leaders
OL,8,Fthere "will be no more rewards for
OL,9,Ffailure" as he set out a package of
OL,10,Fmeasures aimed at tackling poor
OL,11,Fperformance.
OL,13,FStreeting said: "We are announcing the
OL,14,Freforms to make sure every penny of
OL,15,Fextra investment is well spent and
OL,16,Fcuts waiting times for patients.
