OL,6,FTurnaround teams will be sent to
OL,7,Ftrusts that have big financial
OL,8,Fdeficits or are offering patients a
OL,9,Fpoor service.
OL,11,FPoorly performing hospitals will be
OL,12,Fnamed and shamed, meanwhile, the best
OL,13,FNHS performers will be given more
OL,14,Fcontrol over spending to help
OL,15,Fmodernise their buildings, equipment
OL,16,Fand technology.
