OL,3,CFailing hospitals in England to be
OL,4,Cnamed and shamed in league tables
OL,6,FThe Department of Health argues this
OL,7,Fwill benefit top-performing trusts as
OL,8,Funder the current system there is
OL,9,Flittle incentive for trusts to run
OL,10,Fbudget surpluses as they are unable to
OL,11,Fbenefit from them.
OL,13,FNHS leaders have expressed concerns
OL,14,Fthat the move could demoralise staff,
OL,15,Fwith Nuffield Trust's chief executive,
OL,16,FThea Stein, accusing ministers of
OL,17,F"falling for the appealing notion of a
OL,18,Fmagic productivity tree which will
OL,19,Fmake the NHS more efficient just by
OL,20,Fshaking the magic tree harder."
